{"tid":1327630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"野餐成班人一齊玩下小遊戲","createTime":"2019-07-17T16:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T16:24:58.000Z","uid":151338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"af01ee76a44dd9b86a3b4e6bbb753a7c3d580567","tid":1327630,"uid":151338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"次次去野餐果陣都想搵啲野玩下無咁悶<br />\n就諗起懷舊遊戲彈波子<br />\n一黎波子體積細 易攜帶<br />\n二黎又平<br />\n三黎我帶玩具出街都好正常<br />\n四黎我發覺我屋企啲汪汪好鍾意玩球類物體 可以同汪汪同樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次夢遊去左沙田同睇以前汪汪啲笑片<br />\n唔知係汪汪身體結構問題定佢地啲鞋仔問題<br />\n發覺啲汪汪個下盤都好唔穩下<br />\n次次同啲汪汪玩<br />\n佢沖過黎果陣我就撒一堆波子係地下<br />\n轉身就走<br />\n望住佢地仆下仆下個樣我都不自禁偷笑<br />\n不過係草地唔係好啱玩<br />\n<br />\n近排見好似興起番波子棋<br />\n建議下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf5becb8d34e5e3ed84bcc6080dcf82dee3294c","tid":1327630,"uid":151338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"習思廣益諗諗新玩法"},{"pid":"01a8b041ada210166d177c7bde9e7011ec99fb08","tid":1327630,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"走既時候 傷及其他人 要考慮"},{"pid":"fcc6bd6887f1e54750e6445e5267fab9d99e99ff","tid":1327630,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"【\b721文宣】星期日前一齊做鍵盤戰士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327641</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXAdLRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXAdLRx.jpg&h=988ba3dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw6P3Dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw6P3Dd.jpg&h=545a2bea&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxBsQid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxBsQid.jpg&h=0a25f5ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEt65Rz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb